        <h3>~fb7bb1;說~fm3bb1; ㄕㄨㄛ~fb7bb1;時~fm3bb1; ㄕˊ~fb7bb1;遲~fm3bb1; ㄔˊ~fb7bb1;、那~fm3bb1; ㄋㄚˇ~fb7bb1;時~fm3bb1; ㄕˊ~fb7bb1;快~fm3bb1; ㄎㄨㄞˋ~fm3bb1;</h3>
